Video footage circulating on social media surfaced on Wednesday, showing the damages caused to cars by rocks being thrown near the KG Mall, eMalahleni. It is assumed that the rocks were thrown on Tuesday night, after a training facilitator at Samancor, Mr Barries Barnard, confirmed that he suffered under the attack on his commute home from Pretoria. •Read the full story in this Friday’s issue of the Middelburg Observer. 